N2  - Porter's (1980) and Abell's (1980) attempts to classify business strategies have several fundamental limitations After discussing the objectives and attributes of ?scientific? classification systems, this article presents a new classification scheme, built on the work of Porter and Abell, as a first step toward developing an ?optimal? business strategy classification system.
